//! `primitive_dihedral_signature`, etc.).
//!
//! # Resolvers (v0.2.2 W12)
//!
//! Verdict-producing resolvers are free functions in module-per-resolver
//! organization. Each function returns a `Result<Certified<Cert>, Witness>`:
//!
